{"tid":615400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葛珮帆再接死亡恐嚇信　稱「你會死」","createTime":"2018-04-03T10:42:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-03T23:53:08.000Z","uid":41404,"like":87,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"5f47de6bb73c8d73ee5ddd97f482c5806c0a0211","tid":615400,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T10:42:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180403/photo/bkn-20180403174718347-0403_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180403181704\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180403%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180403174718347-0403_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180403181704&h=8fc58475&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n葛珮帆接獲死亡恐嚇，大字寫明「你會死！」(受訪者提供/資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n繼律政司司長鄭若驊、兩名選舉主任及多名立法會議員上月底收到來自日本的恐嚇信後，立法會議員葛珮帆今天(3日)再收到由香港寄出的死亡恐嚇信。寄信人除於信中用大字寫上「你會死！」文中更稱會暗殺你，及要求葛珮帆就上星期的恐嚇信報案銷案，否則「後果自負」。葛珮帆的議員辦事處職員已報案。 <br />\n<br />\n該封手寫恐嚇信又提及會派人殺死葛珮帆的朋友，監視她的一舉一動，及派人暗殺葛珮帆。葛珮帆向東網表示，發信者非常無聊及幼稚，惟接連收到死亡恐嚇信件令辦事處職員受驚，且恐嚇是非常嚴重刑事罪行，絕不能縱容。據悉，警方今天曾到葛珮帆的議員辦事處搜證。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180403/mobile/bkn-20180403174718347-0403_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180403%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180403174718347-0403_00822_001.html&d=mwDQPt1y6DjBgKsiltFnrkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=75b9d4b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180403/mobile/bkn-20180403174718347-0403_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"bc46289c5a04c951b49cacb4a7f099a5d1a79fc0","tid":615400,"uid":122,"like":160,"dislike":0,"score":160,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T10:44:21.000Z","msg":"人人都會"},{"pid":"a3b8a3f824f9f6c291066af0b9b7eee8d5569445","tid":615400,"uid":31237,"like":106,"dislike":1,"score":105,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T10:45:23.000Z","msg":"佢覺得自己永遠都唔會死？"},{"pid":"82334922fb1710faeb41f088ee2ba1f6054aec48","tid":615400,"uid":144024,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T10:46:43