ssets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee362d88904426c9407680707c4d1f839f5d1457","tid":615400,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T10:54:40.000Z","msg":"你以為自己係耶穌？"},{"pid":"868ec91298217898e7917c09fdd48854e896cf25","tid":615400,"uid":113610,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T10:55:50.000Z","msg":"癌細胞 呢 就唔會死既"},{"pid":"bb14c0e1b7bf850d7a9dc448f07ce32e57feec4e","tid":615400,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T10:56:57.000Z","msg":"你唔會死！"},{"pid":"6a8db2c1512c6eb755c5678c87163d3eb1b8dc01","tid":615400,"uid":76115,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T10:57:03.000Z","msg":"我夢見自己正在小學校的講堂上預備作文，向老師請教立論的方法。<br />\n　　「難！」老師從眼鏡圈外斜射出眼光來，看著我，說。「我告訴你一件事&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n　　「一家人家生了一個男孩，合家高興透頂了。滿月的時候，抱出來給客人看，&mdash;&mdash;大概自然是想得一點好兆頭。<br />\n　　「一個說：&lsquo;這孩子將來要發財的。&rsquo;他於是得到一番感謝。<br />\n　　「一個說：&lsquo;這孩子將來是要死的。&rsquo;他於是得到一頓大家合力的痛打。<br />\n　　「說要死的必然，說富貴的許謊。但說謊的得好報，說必然的遭打。你&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n　　「我願意既不說謊，也不遭打。那麼，老師，我得怎么說呢？」<br />\n　　「那麼，你得說：&lsquo;啊呀！這孩子呵！您瞧！那麼&hellip;&hellip;。阿唷！哈哈！Heh e！he，he he he he！&rsquo;」"},{"pid":"763c049d45f27807ec2f1237eef54c496896d47a","tid":615400,"uid":52358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T10:58:38.000Z","msg":"佢係咪中咗丁浩兩掌<br />\n你已經死了（xx年後）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0f5fe5e2bce182bbe0f7e9b2209748bd996377e","tid":615400,"uid":79959,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T11:03:44.000Z","msg":"其實會唔會之前周庭做過個日本訪問，恐嚇信係日本friends 寄?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c92bb340815cf8bdac8627b52ba056fe54f6b43b","tid":615400,"uid":55851,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T11:04:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-cdn.9gag.com/photo/aDzb9Ax_700b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3